      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so my dentist put me on metronidazole for this tooth infection i have and im supposed to take it for a week. i was wondering if its okay to have like 1 or 2 glasses of wine with my dinner tonight? or do i have to wait till i finish the whole course of pills?",
